    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Bamboo- or cane-colored porcelain biscuit, invented by Wedgwood. For objects made from woven or carved bamboo, use "bamboo work (visual works)."</Note_Text>
